MobileCreateRecallNoticeFromReporter is a CompositeForm
    use for action Pending.RecallPortalCreate
    use for smartphone
    title is "Notice"
    called out actions only
    suppress standard toolbar
    show panel navigation
    Actions
        action is refresh
            label is "_"
    NoticeInformation is a Panel
        mouse over text is "PleaseEnterTheFollowingDetailsRelatedToTheNoticeThatYouAreReporting"
        panel header is "PleaseEnterTheFollowingDetailsRelatedToTheNoticeThatYouAreReporting"
        form is MobilePortalRecallNotice
        save on next
    ProductInformation is a Panel
        mouse over text is "PleaseEnterProductInformationRelatedToTheNoticeThatYouAreReporting"
        panel header is "PleaseEnterProductInformationRelatedToTheNoticeThatYouAreReporting"
        list is RecallProduct set.MobilePortalRecallProducts
    Attachments is a Panel
        mouse over text is "PleaseEnterAttachmentsRelatedToTheNoticeThatYouAreReporting"
        panel header is "PleaseEnterAttachmentsRelatedToTheNoticeThatYouAreReporting"
        list is RecallNoticeReference set.MobilePortalRecallReferences
    Summary is a Panel
        visible when (RecallNotice entered)
        form is PortalSummary
